<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
</head>
<style>
    /* Hero section styles */
.hero {
    background: #f9f9f9;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    flex: 1;
}

.hero h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.hero p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
}

.hero .btn {
    background: #4CAF50;
    color: white;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 5px;
}

.hero .btn:hover {
    background: #45a049;
}

/* Section styles */
section {
    padding: 2rem;
}

section h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

section p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

/* Service cards */
.service-card {
    background: #f1f1f1;
    padding: 1rem;
    margin: 1rem 0;
    border-radius: 5px;
    text-align: center;
}

.service-card h3 {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}
</style>
<body>

    <section id="about">
        <h2>About Us</h2>
        <p>Medicare is dedicated to providing top-notch healthcare services to everyone. Our team of professionals is here to support you every step of the way.</p>
    </section>
    
</body>
</html>